results.title: IPhone Eye Dock valet - iphone 4, 4s, 5, 5s, 5c
results.description:
This iPhone 4, 4s, 5, dock/ valet was designed to accept apple IPhones with a case up to an Otterbox Defender in size. This dock also feature a convenient place to store eyeglasses or sun glasses. Wallets can be stowed away securely in a slot to the side of the dock. There is also plenty of storage at the rear of the dock for pocket items.    

The details: 

Easy access to all buttons and phone removal 

Unique charging cable cutout allows both Iphone 4 and 5 cables.  

Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock/valet. 

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets. 

Item ships USPS priority 2 to 3 day mail

This is meant to be used with an iphone 4, 4s, and 5 with a case. Please see our other listings for case-free docking solutions. 

This docking station has been sanded smooth to a soft to the touch finish. We also make this docking station with a boiled linseed oil finish.

Aprx. 7 inches tall x 9.5 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 9.5 inches.  

Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz
